OL,3,CReform UK councillors pick Jex Parkin
OL,4,Cas Birmingham leader
OL,6,FReform UK councillors in Birmingham
OL,7,Fhave selected Jex Parkin as the
OL,8,Fparty's leader on the city council
OL,9,Ffollowing last week's local elections.
OL,11,FParkin, who represents Kingstanding,
OL,12,Fwas elected alongside around 20 other
OL,13,FReform UK councillors as the party
OL,14,Fmade major gains across the city on
OL,15,FThursday.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/3
