OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F371A1778529953
OL,3,CReform UK councillors pick Jex Parkin
OL,4,Cas Birmingham leader
OL,6,FThe result leaves Reform as the
OL,7,Flargest group on Birmingham City
OL,8,FCouncil, but still well short of the
OL,9,F51 seats needed to secure an outright
OL,10,Fmajority and take control of the
OL,11,Fauthority.
OL,13,FCharles Latchford, who represents
OL,14,FLongbridge & West Heath, was selected
OL,15,Fas deputy leader.
OL,17,FThe Liberal Democrats and Greens have
OL,18,Falready ruled out working with Reform
OL,19,FUK in a coalition, raising questions
OL,20,Fover whether the party will be able to
OL,21,Fform an administration.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/3
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
