OL,3,CReform UK councillors pick Jex Parkin
OL,4,Cas Birmingham leader
OL,6,FEven if Reform were able to reach an
OL,7,Fagreement with the Conservatives, the
OL,8,Fcombined numbers would still fall
OL,9,Fshort of a majority in the council
OL,10,Fchamber.
OL,12,FThe next full council meeting to
OL,13,Fdecide the council leader is on
OL,14,FTuesday, 19th May.
